析的安全数学表达式求值服务，规避eval风险，支持括号优先级与异常防护。","descriptionEn":"计算四则运算表达式\n    参数:\n        expression: 数学表达式字符串，如 \"1 + 2 * 3\"\n    返回:\n        计算结果\n\npython\ndef calculate_expression(expression):\n    try:\n        # 使用 eval 函数计算表达式\n        result = eval(expression)\n        return result\n    except Exception as e:\n        # 如果表达式有误，返回错误信息\n        return str(e)\n\n# 示例\nprint(calculate_expression(\"1 + 2 * 3\"))  # 输出: 7\nprint(calculate_expression(\"(1 + 2) * 3\"))  # 输出: 9\nprint(calculate_expression(\"1 / 0\"))  # 输出: division by zero\n\n\n请注意，使用 `eval` 函数可能存在安全风险，因为它会执行传入的字符串作为 Python 代码。在实际应用中，请确保输入是可信的，或者考虑使用更安全的解析库来处理数学表达式。","category":"other","tags":["安全计算","AST解析","Python实现","MCP测试","教学示例"],"version":"0.0.0","npmPackage":"test2test2-calc1","securityScore":60,"requiresApiKey":false,"platforms":["linux","macos","windows"],"isOfficial":false,"isNew":false,"toolCount":0,"installStatus":"not_installed","installable":true,"installMethod":"pypi","sourceUrl":"https://github.com/lcc-ops/evil_mcp","source":"modelscope","configHint":"默认禁用eval，采用ast.literal_eval+自定义运算符解析器","envSchema":{},"envRequired":[],"isVerified":false,"isHosted":false,"capabilities":["代码教学","MCP协议验证","安全计算实验"]},{"serverId":"ericwyn-cal-tool","friendlyName":"全能数学计算器","friendlyNameEn":"数学表达式计算器","description":"支持三角函数、幂运算、常数π/e及变量代入的增强型表达式计算器，兼容MCP协议调用。","descriptionEn":"一个简单的命令行工具，用于计算数学表达式，支持mcp模式和广泛的数学运算。","category":"other","tags":["科学计算","符号运算","MCP工具","CLI工具","数学函数"],"version":"0.0.0","npmPackage":"ericwyn-cal-tool","securityScore":60,"requiresApiKey":false,"platforms":["linux","macos","windows"],"isOfficial":false,"isNew":false,"toolCount":0,"installStatus":"not_installed","installable":false,"installMethod":"none","sourceUrl":"https://github.com/Ericwyn/cal-tool","source":"modelscope","configHint":"内置math模块扩展，支持自定义函数注册","envSchema":{},"envRequired":[],"isVerified":false,"isHosted":false,"capabilities":["数据分析预处理","工程计算","AI工作流函数"]},{"serverId":"cayenne-cayenne","friendlyName":"黄历吉凶查询","friendl